ris Brown Drops 'Look At Me Now', Featuring Lil Wayne, Busta Rhymes|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1655216/chris-brown-drops-look-at-me-now-featuring-lil-wayne-busta-rhymes.jhtml|accessdate=2011-01-14|newspaper=MTV News|date=2011-01-03|archive-date=2013-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131030132252/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1655216/chris-brown-drops-look-at-me-now-featuring-lil-wayne-busta-rhymes.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>该曲的榜单表现不俗，在公告牌节奏布鲁斯/嘻哈榜和说唱榜上都登上榜首，在百强单曲榜上最高达到第六。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/#/song/chris-brown-featuring-lil-wayne-busta-rhymes/look-at-me-now/25163288|title=Look At Me Now - Chris Brown|publisher=Billboard.com|accessdate=2010-02-03|archive-date=2011-10-13|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/62OtgJtp1?url=http://www.billboard.com/#/song/chris-brown-featuring-lil-wayne-busta-rhymes/look-at-me-now/25163288|dead-url=no}}</ref>该专辑的第三、第四支单曲分别为“Beautiful People”和“She Ain't You”。为推广专辑，布朗将从2011年4月开始举行巡演，首站在澳大利亚。<ref name="FAME tour">{{cite web |last=Cashmere |first=Paul |url=http://www.undercover.fm/news/13434-chris-brown-aussie-tour-announced |title=Undercover News: Chris Brown Aussie Tour announced |work=Undercover |date=2011-01-20 |accessdate=2011-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110121035557/http://www.undercover.fm/news/13434-chris-brown-aussie-tour-announced |archive-date=2011-01-21 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

