== 个人形象与私生活 ==
===  成功及同他人的比较 ===
除了在独唱方面获得成功外，布朗还曾与其他歌手合作演绎过不少打榜歌曲：如和[[喬丁·斯帕克斯|喬丁·斯帕克斯]]合作的“No Air”，和[[说唱歌手|说唱歌手]][[鲍沃|鲍沃]]合作演绎的“Shortie like Mine”，以及和[[Lil_Mama|Lil Mama]]与[[T-Pain|T-Pain]]共同演唱的“Shawty Get Loose”。三首歌曲在[[公告牌百强单曲榜|公告牌百强单曲榜]]分别获得第三、第九、第十的成绩。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/bbcom/charts/chart_display.jsp?f=Pop+100&pageNumber=Top+11-50&g=Singles |title=Billboard - Updated Album Charts from the most Trusted Music Magazine |accessdate=2010-02-03 |archive-date=2008-10-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081005075106/http://www.billboard.com/bbcom/charts/chart_display.jsp?f=Pop+100&pageNumber=Top+11-50&g=Singles |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>[http://acharts.us/song/11170 Shortie like Mine Chart Track] {{Wayback|url=http://acharts.us/song/11170 |date=20080914230455 }}. ''Accharts.'' Accessed August 16, 2008.</ref><ref>[http://acharts.us/song/33939 Lil Mama and Chris Brown - Shawty Get Loose - Music Charts] {{Wayback|url=http://acharts.us/song/33939 |date=20080914230505 }}. ''Accharts.'' Accessed August 16, 2008.</ref>

布朗擅长跳舞，这一点常常被拿来和知名节奏布鲁斯艺术家[[亚瑟小子|亚瑟小子]]、[[迈克尔·杰克逊|迈克尔·杰克逊]]比较，布朗自己也提及两人对自己的音乐有很大影响。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://new.music.yahoo.com/blogs/hiphopmediatraining/19398/usher-has-chris-brown-taken-your-spot|title=Usher, Has Chris Brown Taken Your Spot?|author=Billy Johnson, Jr.|publisher=[http://music.yahoo.com/ Yahoo! Music]|date=2008-05-01|accessdate=2008-08-16|archive-date=2008-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080516110652/http://new.music.yahoo.com/blogs/hiphopmediatraining/19398/usher-has-chris-brown-taken-your-spot/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 家庭暴力案件 ===
2009年2月8日，布朗向[[洛杉矶警察局|洛杉矶警察局]]威尔夏（Wilshire）分局自首，并因其犯罪恐吓被收押。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eonline.com/uberblog/b99069_chris_brown_arrested_after_alleged.html|title=Chris Brown Arrested After Alleged Rihanna Assault|last=Errico|first=Marcus|date=2009-02-08|work=[[E!_Online|E! Online]]|publisher=[[E!|E! Online]]|accessdate=2009-02-08|archive-date=2011-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110730091004/http://www.eonline.com/uberblog/b99069_chris_brown_arrested_after_alleged.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>据称布朗正在接受对其[[家庭暴力|家庭暴力]]的调查，施暴对象是某女性。警方的报告中并没有公布该名女性的姓名，但称其“遭受了明显的创伤”。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cnn.com/2009/SHOWBIZ/Music/02/09/chris.brown/index.html?iref=mpstoryview#cnnSTCText|title=Sources: Brown's alleged victim was girlfriend Rihanna|accessdate=2010-02-03|archive-date=2019-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190411214504/http://www.cnn.com/2009/SHOWBIZ/Music/02/09/chris.brown/index.html?iref=mpstoryview#cnnSTCText|dead-url=no}}</ref>但是根据多家新闻媒体，如《洛杉矶时报》、[[CNN|CNN]]、[[MSNBC|MSNBC]]称，有消息知名这位据称的受害者就是布朗的女友、节奏布鲁斯歌手[[蕾哈娜|蕾哈娜]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/29088387/|title=Brown arrested after alleged attack on Rihanna|accessdate=2009-03-13|publisher=MSNBC|date=2009-02-09|archive-date=2009-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091213151245/http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/29088387/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/lanow/2009/02/chris-brown-boo.html |title= Singer Chris Brown under investigation in alleged assault |accessdate= 2009-03-13 |publisher= Los Angeles Times |date= 2009-02-08 |archive-date= 2020-07-31 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200731164246/https://latimesblogs.latimes.com/lanow/2009/02/chris-brown-boo.html |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref name="Schreffler">{{cite web |url=http://www.nydailynews.com/gossip/2009/02/08/2009-02-08_chris_brown_sought_by_police_in_battery_.html |title=Chris Brown sought by police in battery investigation |last=Schreffler |first=Laura |coauthors=Yaniv, Oren |date=2009-02-08 |work=[[Daily_News_(New_York)|Daily News]] |publisher=[[Mortimer_Zuckerman|Mortimer Zuckerman]] |accessdate=2009-02-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090418224830/http://www.nydailynews.com/gossip/2009/02/08/2009-02-08_chris_brown_sought_by_police_in_battery_.html |archivedate=2009-04-18 }}</ref>在布朗被捕后，多个他的商业广告被叫停，音乐也从广播电台中撤掉，他完全从公众视野中消失。原定参加表演的[[第51屆葛萊美獎|第51屆葛萊美獎]]也由[[賈斯汀·提姆布萊克|賈斯汀·提姆布萊克]]和[[艾尔·格林|艾尔·格林]]顶替。<ref name="Schreffler"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eonline.com/uberblog/b99243_chris_brown_bounces_nba_all-star.html|title=Chris Brown Lowdown: Cops Continue Probe, Wrigley Halts Ads|last=Grossberg|first=Josh|coauthors=Errico, Marcus|date=2009-02-09|work=E! Online|publisher=E! Online|accessdate=2009-02-09|archive-date=2011-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110402151827/http://www.eonline.com/uberblog/b99243_chris_brown_bounces_nba_all-star.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.entertainmentwise.com/new/47079/chris-brown-got-milk-ad-dropped-as-radio-station-bans-his-records|title=Chris Brown 'Got Milk' Ad Dropped As Radio Station Bans His Records}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://hollywoodinsider.ew.com/2009/02/chris-brown-and.html |title=Chris Brown and Rihanna: More fallout |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090213111742/http://hollywoodinsider.ew.com/2009/02/chris-brown-and.html |archivedate=2009-02-13 |accessdate=2010-02-03 }}</ref>布朗后来发表声明称：“对于发生的事，言语已经无法表达我的歉意和悲伤。”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://gawker.com/5154020/chris-brown-sorry-about-rihanna-incident |title=Chris Brown Sorry About Rihanna Incident |last=Tate |first=Ryan |date=February 15, 2009 |publisher=Gawker |accessdate=2009-03-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090311052840/http://gawker.com/5154020/chris-brown-sorry-about-rihanna-incident |archivedate=2009-03-11 }}</ref>

2009年3月5日，布朗被指控袭击并恐吓他人。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.findlaw.com/hdocs/docs/crim/chris-brown-rihanna-felony-assault-charges.html|title=Felony Complaint (People v. Christopher Brown|date=2009-03-05|publisher=FindLaw|accessdate=2009-03-05|archive-date=2017-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170714221809/http://news.findlaw.com/hdocs/docs/crim/chris-brown-rihanna-felony-assault-charges.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1606372/20090305/brown__chris__18_.jhtml|title=Chris Brown Charged With Felony Assault, Making Criminal Threats|last=Kaufman|first=Gil|date=2009-03-05|work=MTV|accessdate=2009-03-05|archive-date=2010-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100109211701/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1606372/20090305/brown__chris__18_.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>他于2009年4月6日被提讯，辩称自己无罪。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/2009/SHOWBIZ/Music/04/06/chris.brown/index.html|title=Chris Brown pleads not guilty in assault case|date=2009-04-07|publisher=CNN|accessdate=2009-06-08|archive-date=2020-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200915044745/http://www.cnn.com/2009/SHOWBIZ/Music/04/06/chris.brown/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>但在2009年6月22日的庭审中，布朗认罪，并接受了社区劳动与5年缓刑辩诉交易。同时法官还当庭要求布朗接受家庭暴力方面的咨询辅导。<ref>[http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/lanow/2009/06/settlement-might-be-near-in-chris-brown-case.html Settlement reached in Chris Brown's alleged beating of Rihanna] {{Wayback|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/lanow/2009/06/settlement-might-be-near-in-chris-brown-case.html |date=20180915182742 }}, ''Los Angeles Times'', June 22, 2009</ref>部分反对家庭暴力的组织对该辩诉交易表示不满，认为对布朗的处罚不足；布朗的童年经历对其的影响也被拿来仔细审视。<ref>{{citation|last=Melago|first=Carrie|title=Chris Brown plea deal in Rihanna beating sends bad message, say domestic abuse experts|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/gossip/2009/06/24/2009-06-24_chris_brown_plea_deal_in_rihanna_beating_sends_bad_message_says_domestic_abuse_e.html|newspaper=[[Daily_News_(New_York)|Daily News]]|date=2009-06-24|accessdate=2009-07-20|archive-date=2009-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090822090514/http://www.nydailynews.com/gossip/2009/06/24/2009-06-24_chris_brown_plea_deal_in_rihanna_beating_sends_bad_message_says_domestic_abuse_e.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{citation|last1=Brown|first1=DeNeen|last2=Surdin|first2=Ashley|title=Chris Brown Pleads Guilty to Assault|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2009/06/22/AR2009062200452.html?wprss=rss_print/style|newspaper=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|date=2009-06-23|accessdate=2009-07-20|archive-date=2018-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180915182643/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2009/06/22/AR2009062200452.html?wprss=rss_print%2Fstyle|dead-url=no}}</ref>2009年7月20日，布朗在其[[YouTube|YouTube]]页面上发布了一份两分钟的视频，向歌迷和蕾哈娜表示歉意，对这次事件他“追悔莫及”，并称自己已反复向蕾哈娜道歉，并会“担起一切责任”。<ref name="youtube.com">{{cite news|title=A Message From Chris|publisher=[[YouTube|YouTube]]/Chris Brown Official Channel|date=2009-07-20|accessdate=2009-07-20|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n4SD6oBvbKY|archive-date=2019-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191130004514/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n4SD6oBvbKY|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="wonderwall.msn.com">{{cite news|title=Chris Brown apologizes for Rihanna beating|publisher=[[MSN|MSN]]|date=2009-07-20|accessdate=2009-07-20|url=http://wonderwall.msn.com/#wallState=0__/music/chris-brown-apologizes-or-rihanna-beating-1518453.story|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090709063455/http://wonderwall.msn.com//#wallState=0__/music/chris-brown-apologizes-or-rihanna-beating-1518453.story|archivedate=2009-07-09}}</ref><ref name="Mtv.com">{{cite news|first=Jayson|last=Rodriguez|title=Chris Brown Apologizes For Rihanna Assault In New Video|publisher=[[MTV|MTV]]|date=2009-07-20|accessdate=2009-07-20|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1616575/20090720/brown__chris__18_.jhtml|archive-date=2010-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100109233014/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1616575/20090720/brown__chris__18_.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>布朗说他早先希望对该案作出解释，但他的律师建议等判决下来之后在进行不迟。 <ref name=youtube.com/><ref name=wonderwall.msn.com/><ref name=Mtv.com/>8月25日，布朗被判5年[[缓刑|缓刑]]、一年家庭暴力咨询以及6个月的社区服务；法官还签署了一份长达5年的[[限制令|限制令]]，要求其至少与蕾哈娜保持100码的距离，在公共活动时也必须保持10码的距离。<ref>{{cite news|first=Anthony|last=McCartney|title=Chris Brown sentenced in Rihanna assault case|agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|date=2009-09-25|accessdate=2009-09-25|url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5jd7tN4gXF5Ta8eaVJfsc_n3pBFfAD9AA6DTO0}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Chris Brown sentenced for Rihanna assault|url=http://www.cnn.com/2009/CRIME/08/25/chris.brown.sentencing/|publisher=[[CNN|CNN]]|date=2009-09-25|accessdate=2009-09-25|archive-date=2020-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200928164642/https://www.cnn.com/2009/CRIME/08/25/chris.brown.sentencing/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Chris Brown sentenced to community labour in Rihanna assault case|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/celebritynews/6090224/Chris-Brown-sentenced-to-community-labour-in-Rihanna-assault-case.html|publisher=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]]|date=2009-09-25|accessdate=2009-09-25|archive-date=2010-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100915160524/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/celebritynews/6090224/Chris-Brown-sentenced-to-community-labour-in-Rihanna-assault-case.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2009年9月2日，布朗就家庭暴力案件接受“[[拉里金现场|拉里金现场]]”（Larry King Live）节目的采访，访谈采取预先录制的办法，这是他在此事后的首次公开亮相。<ref name="www.cnn.com">{{cite news|first=Amy|last=Huggins|title=Chris Brown says he still loves Rihanna|publisher=[[CNN|CNN]]|date=2009-08-31|accessdate=2009-09-03|url=http://www.cnn.com/2009/SHOWBIZ/Music/08/31/chris.brown.interview/index.html|archive-date=2020-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200915044800/http://www.cnn.com/2009/SHOWBIZ/Music/08/31/chris.brown.interview/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="www.msnbc.msn.com">{{cite news|title=Yes, Chris Brown remembers Rihanna beating|publisher=[[MSNBC|MSNBC]]|date=2009-09-01|accessdate=2009-09-03|url=http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/32634846/ns/entertainment-celebrities/|archive-date=2009-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090904225017/http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/32634846/ns/entertainment-celebrities/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="www.rollingstone.com">{{cite news|title=Chris Brown Clarifies King Interview, Says He Recalls Rihanna Incident|publisher=''[[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]]''|date=2009-09-01|accessdate=2009-09-03|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/rockdaily/index.php/2009/09/01/chris-brown-denies-he-cant-recall-rihanna-incident/|archive-date=2009-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090908003738/http://www.rollingstone.com/rockdaily/index.php/2009/09/01/chris-brown-denies-he-cant-recall-rihanna-incident/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="www.nydailynews.com">{{cite news|first=Issie|last=Lapowsky|title=Chris Brown on 'Larry King Live': Relationship with Rihanna 'was sort of like Romeo and Juliet'|publisher=''[[Daily_News_(New_York)|New Your Daily News]]''|date=2009-08-31|accessdate=2009-09-03|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/gossip/2009/09/03/2009-09-03_chris_brown_on_larry_king_live_relationship_with_rihanna_was_sort_of_like_romeo_.html#ixzz0Q5q2qUHR|archive-date=2009-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090906103831/http://www.nydailynews.com/gossip/2009/09/03/2009-09-03_chris_brown_on_larry_king_live_relationship_with_rihanna_was_sort_of_like_romeo_.html#ixzz0Q5q2qUHR|dead-url=no}}</ref>同他一起上节目的还有他的母亲和律师马克·格拉格斯（Mark Geragos）。布朗本人谈起自己成长于家庭暴力猖獗的环境中；其母经常受到继父的殴打。布朗说当他得知袭击案当晚的细节，自己对蕾哈娜的身体伤害时：“我完全震惊了，因为，首先，那不是真正的我，我也不希望成为那样的人。”<ref name=www.cnn.com/>布朗的母亲乔伊斯·霍金斯则说布朗“从来都不是一个暴力分子，从来不是”，她也不相信所谓的“暴力循环理论”（cycle of violence）。<ref name=www.cnn.com/>布朗称在媒体大肆报道家庭暴力案时，自己和蕾哈娜的关系仍像[[罗密欧与朱丽叶|罗密欧与朱丽叶]]，而最终是跟踪报道这些新闻的媒体拆散了他们。<ref name=www.nydailynews.com/>他表示自己并不记得袭击了蕾哈娜，但意识到这件事情发生了，并为自己当晚的行为表示道歉。<ref name=www.cnn.com/><ref name=www.msnbc.msn.com/><ref name=www.rollingstone.com/><ref name=www.nydailynews.com/><ref name="www.usmagazine.com">{{cite news|title=Chris Brown: I Don't Remember Beating Rihanna|publisher=''[[Us_Weekly|Us Weekly]]''|date=2009-08-31|accessdate=2009-09-03|url=http://www.usmagazine.com/news/chris-brown-i-dont-remember-beating-rihanna-2009318|archive-date=2009-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090902105547/http://www.usmagazine.com/news/chris-brown-i-dont-remember-beating-rihanna-2009318|dead-url=no}}</ref>面对针对他称自己什么都不记得的指责，布朗随后表示：“我的确记得发生过什么。在采访中我母亲曾多次说，我在袭击案后立刻去找了她，并告诉她发生的一切。”布朗说尽管如此，“（那一晚）依旧是模糊不清的。” <ref name=www.msnbc.msn.com/><ref name=www.rollingstone.com/>在节目中，他表示蕾哈娜遭袭击后的照片或许会始终萦绕在他的脑海中，看到这张照片对他来讲“很痛苦”，他仍然爱着蕾哈娜。<ref name name=www.cnn.com/> “我很确信我们可以继续做朋友，”布朗说，“虽然我不清楚我们的恋爱关系如何，但我知道我们最终绝对是朋友。”此外，他并不认为自己的明星之路已经走到尽头。<ref name=www.nydailynews.com/>

布朗于2009年12月4日在电视节目《20/20》接受了深度访问。在接受《[[早安美国|早安美国]]》主持人{{link-en|罗宾·罗伯斯|Robin Roberts (newscaster)}}采访时，他进一步谈论了对蕾哈娜的袭击案。<ref name="Www.rollingstone.com">{{cite news|title=<nowiki>Chris Brown Tells “20/20″ That Rihanna Cried After Hearing “Changed Man”</nowiki>|publisher=''[[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]]''|date=2009-12-04|accessdate=2009-12-04|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/rockdaily/index.php/2009/12/04/chris-brown-tells-2020-that-rihanna-cried-after-hearing-changed-man/|archive-date=2010-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100210121935/http://www.rollingstone.com/rockdaily/index.php/2009/12/04/chris-brown-tells-2020-that-rihanna-cried-after-hearing-changed-man/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2010年6月，布朗为前往[[英国|英国]]申请签证，但因为“有严重犯罪前科”而被拒签。<ref name="BBCVisa">{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment_and_arts/10263828.stm |title=Singer Chris Brown denied entry to the UK |date=2010-06-08 |accessdate=2010-06-08 |publisher=BBC}}</ref>作为欧洲巡演的一部分，布朗原计划前往英国的数个城市演出，但[[索尼|索尼]]表示，因为“工作签证问题”，此次巡演不得不推迟。英国内政部随后确认，布朗被拒签的原因就是因为袭击前女友[[蕾哈娜|蕾哈娜]]而被判有罪。<ref name="BBCVisa"/> <ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/news/chris-brown-denied-u-k-visa-postpones-tour-1004096108.story#/news/chris-brown-denied-u-k-visa-postpones-tour-1004096108.story |title=Billboard关于此事的报道 |accessdate=2010-06-28 |archive-date=2012-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121110031831/http://www.billboard.com/news/chris-brown-denied-u-k-visa-postpones-tour-1004096108.story#/news/chris-brown-denied-u-k-visa-postpones-tour-1004096108.story |dead-url=no }}</ref>

