tainment/drake-not-arrested-and-addresses-chris-brown-fight-nyc-concert-details-jones-beach|dead-url=no}}</ref>而布朗的律师称德雷克挑起了事端。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/report-drake-to-be-charged-in-club-fight-20120616|title=Report: Drake to Be Charged in Club Fight|work=Rolling Stone|date=June 16, 2012|accessdate=2012-09-13|archive-date=2018-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180618052536/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/report-drake-to-be-charged-in-club-fight-20120616|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 其他法律纠纷及入狱 ===
2013年，媒体报道称，布朗提交给法庭的社区服务证明记录上存在疑点。对此地方检察官已经提起动议，要求法官裁定布朗之前的社区服务无效。<ref>[http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/gossip/chris-brown-probation-scam-article-1.1255958 Chris Brown may face jail time for violating probation for failing to complete required community service as part of Rihanna assault case] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/gossip/chris-brown-probation-scam-article-1.1255958 |date=20191014223229 }}, by Nancy Dillon, 5 February 2013, New York Daily News</ref>2013年7月，因涉嫌在洛杉矶交通肇事逃逸，他的保释被取消。布朗被当庭释放，并安排在8月重新开庭受审。<ref>{{cite news|title=Chris Brown has probation revoked and awaits decision on jail|publisher=London Evening Standard|date=July 16, 2013|accessdate=July 17, 2013|url=http://www.standard.co.uk/showbiz/celebrity-news/chris-brown-has-probation-revoked-and-awaits-decision-on-jail-8710287.html|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111202419/https://www.standard.co.uk/showbiz/celebrity-news/chris-brown-has-probation-revoked-and-awaits-decision-on-jail-8710287.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>后来指控被取消，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.xxlmag.com/news/2013/08/chris-browns-hit-and-run-case-dismissed/ |title=Chris Brown's Hit-And-Run Case Dismissed - XXL |publisher=Xxlmag.com |date=2013-08-15 |accessdate=2013-10-28 |archive-date=2019-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190108051515/http://www.xxlmag.com/news/2013/08/chris-browns-hit-and-run-case-dismissed/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>但布朗还是被加罚了1000小时社工。<ref name="autogenerated2">{{cite news |url=http://www.cnn.com/2013/10/28/showbiz/chris-brown-assault-charge/ |title=Assault charge against Chris Brown reduced in D.C. brawl |publisher=CNN |date=2009-09-02 |accessdate=2013-10-29 |archive-date=2020-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201001030600/https://www.cnn.com/2013/10/28/showbiz/chris-brown-assault-charge/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2013年10月27日，布朗因涉嫌袭击重罪在[[华盛顿特区|华盛顿特区]]被捕。据称打斗皆因在W饭店前两名女性希望同布朗合影而起。两名男性看到了布朗，试图一同合影。布朗及其保镖袭击了其中一名男性，据受害者称其鼻子受伤。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.xxlmag.com/news/2013/10/chris-brown-arrested-assault-d-c/ |title=Chris Brown Arrested For Assault In D.C. - XXL |publisher=[[XXL_magazine|XXL magazine]] |date= |accessdate=2013-10-28 |archive-date=2019-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191201133903/https://www.xxlmag.com/news/2013/10/chris-brown-arrested-assault-d-c/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>最初警方报告称布朗的保镖挑起的争斗，后来的报告则称是布朗伤及了对方。<ref>{{cite web |last=Baker |first=Soren |url=http://www.hiphopdx.com/index/news/id.25994/title.chris-brown-did-not-throw-first-punch-in-d-c-incident-initial-police-report-says |title=Chris Brown Did Not Throw First Punch In D.C. Incident, Initial Police Report Says |publisher=HipHop DX |date= |accessdate=2013-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131031150608/http://www.hiphopdx.com/index/news/id.25994/title.chris-brown-did-not-throw-first-punch-in-d-c-incident-initial-police-report-says |archive-date=2013-10-31 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>次日，指控减到了轻罪。<ref name="autogenerated2"/>在袭击他人后，布朗在华盛顿特区监狱中度过了36小时，后被释放，并被法官指令在48小时内向其加州的假释官报道。假释官将想加州法官报告，如果认定布朗违反了假释条件，那么他可能最高被处以4年监禁。<ref name="cnn.com">{{cite web |url=http://www.cnn.com/2013/10/29/showbiz/chris-brown-rehab/index.html |title=Chris Brown heads to rehab; seeks 'insight' into his behavior |publisher=CNN.com |date= |accessdate=2014-02-20 |archive-date=2020-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101125703/https://www.cnn.com/2013/10/29/showbiz/chris-brown-rehab/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>2013年10月30日，布朗自愿进入一家康复中心，并预计会呆3个月。但是11月14日，他因为暴力行为违反康复中心规定而被扫地出门。11月20日，在其假释情况的听证会上，布朗被判要在情绪控制康复中心接受90天治疗，同时必须接受毒品检测并服用中心向其提供的任何药物。在2013年12月的另一次听证会上，布朗的假释判决被取消：法官认为华盛顿特区一案足以证明布朗并没有按要求遵纪守法，但是因为在康复中心表现良好，法官并没有要求将其收押。在完成了90天的康复治疗后，法官判决其继续呆在马里布的一家治疗中心，等待2014年4月23日的听证。2014年3月14日，布朗因违反内部规定被治疗中心扫地出门，并立即被收监。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.xxlmag.com/news/2014/03/chris-brown-going-jail/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-03-28 |archive-date=2019-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191016060141/https://www.xxlmag.com/news/2014/03/chris-brown-going-jail/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cnn.com/2014/03/17/showbiz/chris-brown-jail/index.html?eref=rss_mostpopular |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-03-28 |archive-date=2017-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170823074153/http://www.cnn.com/2014/03/17/showbiz/chris-brown-jail/index.html?eref=rss_mostpopular |dead-url=no }}</ref>原本他预计会在4月23日被释放，<ref>{{cite web |author=Miranda J. |url=http://www.xxlmag.com/news/2014/03/chris-brown-going-jail/ |title=Chris Brown Is Going To Jail - XXL |publisher=Xxlmag.com |date=2014-03-14 |accessdate=2015-03-05 |archive-date=2019-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191016060141/https://www.xxlmag.com/news/2014/03/chris-brown-going-jail/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.cnn.com/2014/03/17/showbiz/chris-brown-jail/index.html?eref=rss_mostpopular | work=CNN | title=Judge orders Chris Brown to stay in jail - CNN.com | date=March 18, 2014 | accessdate=2014-03-28 | archive-date=2017-08-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170823074153/http://www.cnn.com/2014/03/17/showbiz/chris-brown-jail/index.html?eref=rss_mostpopular | dead-url=no }}</ref>但是高等法院法官维克多·格林伯格拒绝其保释请求。<ref>{{cite web |author=Compiled by Tony HicksContra Costa Times |url=http://www.mercurynews.com/entertainment/ci_25629090/chris-brown-denied-release-from-jail |title=Chris Brown denied release from jail - San Jose Mercury News |publisher=Mercurynews.com |date=2014-04-24 |accessdate=2015-03-05 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304031113/http://www.mercurynews.com/entertainment/ci_25629090/chris-brown-denied-release-from-jail |dead-url=no }}</ref>在2014年5月9日的庭审中，布朗因违反假释条款被判入狱131天。他原本的刑期为365天，但是扣除了其在疗养院和监狱中已度过的234天。<ref>{{cite web |last=Nostro |first=Lauren |url=http://www.complex.com/music/2014/05/chris-brown-probation-violation-jail-sentence |title=Chris Brown Will Serve Additional 131 Days in Jail For Probation Violation |publisher=Complex |date=2014-05-09 |accessdate=2015-03-05 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112000235/https://www.complex.com/music/2014/05/chris-brown-probation-violation-jail-sentence |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2014年6月2日，由于监狱过度拥挤，刑期1天计做2天，布朗被提前释放。根据《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》报道：“布朗尚未完全获得自由身。他显然仍处于假释中，而且要每周两次定期见心理医生，完成他剩余的社区服务，服用为其开出的药物并拒绝包括医用在内的大麻使用。根据庭审文件报道，这名歌手有躁鬱症。”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/gossip/la-et-mg-chris-brown-released-from-jail-thanks-god-20140602-story.html|title=Chris Brown is out of the slammer yet again -- the singer was released from jail early Monday due to overcrowding. - Los Angeles Times|last=Saad|first=Nardine|work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|accessdate=4 July 2014|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112012301/https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/gossip/la-et-mg-chris-brown-released-from-jail-thanks-god-20140602-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

